NORMAL MODE
**************************

  MP3 FILES
  ----------------------------

  Frame Mode (VBR file)
  ,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

  OK:

  - EOF with tags version of input file
  - no tags (-n)
  - tags v1 (-T 1)
  - tags v2 (-T 2)
  - tags v1 & v2 (-T 12)
  - no xing (-x)
  - m3u file (-m)
  - output directory (-d)
  - custom tags (-g)
  - overlap splitpoints (-O)
  - stdin : input not seekable (-k)
  - output filename (-o) + create directories
  - stdout (+ multiple splitpoints & EOF)
  - no tags in input file (+ -g option)

  NOT DONE:

  - auto adjust (-a)
  - silence parameters (-a & -p) : th, off, gap
  - don't create 'mp3splt.log' file (-N)


  Non Frame Mode (CBR file)
  ,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

  OK:
  - EOF with tags version of input file
  - no tags (-n)
  - tags v1 (-T 1)
  - tags v2 (-T 2)
  - tags v1 & v2 (-T 12)
  - overlap splitpoints (-O)
  - stdout (+ multiple splitpoints & EOF)

  IN PROGRESS:
  - stdin : input not seekable (-k) (TODO BUGS ?)

  NOT DONE:
  - no xing (-x)
  - m3u file (-m)
  - output directory (-d)
  - custom tags (-g)
  - output filename (-o) + create directories
  - no tags in input file (+ -g option)
  - auto adjust (-a)
  - silence parameters (-a & -p) : th, off, gap
  - don't create 'mp3splt.log' file (-N)

